td.p:
By its application, the European Commission seeks a declaration that the Kingdom of Denmark has failed to fulfil its obligations under Article 2(6) and Article 8 of Regulation (EC) No 1072/2009 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 21 October 2009 on common rules for access to the international road haulage market (
OJ 2009 L 300, p. 72
).
